room_title: Escape room "Locked! at the Bistro!" by Unlocked! Escape Rooms in Andover
room_description: Feeling bold, you and your friends decide to try the local Snooty French Restaurant. However, as you wait for your appetizers, you realize the waiter and chef have left and locked the door behind them! You’re alone and trapped in the cafe! The alarm will go into “Night Mode” in 60 minutes. If you can’t get out in that time, you’ll be trapped overnight with the fresh escargot!
